# Spike-local .gitignore.
#
# The repo's top-level .gitignore already excludes `target/` globally,
# so this file is mostly redundant — kept for clarity so anyone landing
# in this subdir directly (looking at the spike in isolation) sees the
# crate's intent. Convention: bin crates with a committed Cargo.lock,
# explicit /target ignore, no other secrets.

/target

# Editor / OS noise (redundant with root but kept local for clarity)
*.swp
.DS_Store
